{
  "texts": [
    "There are some limitations to our system.",
    "First, the small amount of validation data demands cautiousness when making any claims about the effec-tiveness of ILAP or our scoring functionality.",
    "For this reason, we are striving for wider deployment of the platform to collect data from different and larger groups, for example in schools or learning environments.",
    "Secondly, questions about the effect of the use of technology in the creation of the EIT items remain open.",
    "In the future, we plan to investigate to what extent technology can be used in creating language proficiency test items and the effect on test validity."
  ]
}